<li id="cite_note-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-11">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMcConkie1972" class="citation web cs1"><a href="/wiki/Bruce_R._McConkie" title="Bruce R. McConkie">McConkie, Bruce R.</a> (4 January 1972). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://speeches.byu.edu/talks/bruce-r-mcconkie/the-lord-god-of-joseph-smith/">"The Lord God of Joseph Smith"</a>. <i>BYU Speeches</i>. Provo, Utah: <a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young_University_Press" title="Brigham Young University Press">Brigham Young University Press</a><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">10 August</span> 2021</span>. <q>Speeches of the Year</q></cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=BYU+Speeches&amp;rft.atitle=The+Lord+God+of+Joseph+Smith&amp;rft.date=1972-01-04&amp;rft.aulast=McConkie&amp;rft.aufirst=Bruce+R.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fspeeches.byu.edu%2Ftalks%2Fbruce-r-mcconkie%2Fthe-lord-god-of-joseph-smith%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ALectures+on+Faith" class="Z3988"></span></span>
